WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.500
When we stop listening, we stop learning.

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:09.000
When we stop learning, we stop growing.

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:15.000
And when we stop growing, we begin to die — intellectually and emotionally.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
That's why critical thinking matters.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.000
Not to win debates, but to grow as a person.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:29.000
Welcome to Lojik360.
